     get access to this class, use the following segment of code:
<programlisting>
import org.postgresql.largeobject.*;
Connection  conn;
LargeObjectManager lobj;
// ... code that opens a connection ...
lobj = ((org.postgresql.Connection)myconn).getLargeObjectAPI();
</programlisting>
    </para>

    <para>
